column9: Avantair, Inc. is a Delaware corporation and was organized in 2004. Avantair, Inc. and its subsidiaries (the "Company" or "Avantair") are in the business of providing private aviation services through three primary flight service programs: (i) the sale of fractional ownership interests through the Fractional Ownership program; (ii) the lease of fractional interests through the Axis Lease program; and (iii) the sale of flight hour cards through the Edge Card program.
